# Local stats artifacts — re-generated by /tene-stats. The accumulated
# main report and per-run snapshots change every refresh and add diff
# noise without project value. Keep them out of the repo.
docs/stats/github-stats.md
docs/stats/snapshots/

# Local product intro export — generated on demand from internal docs,
